[Many thanks to Ivan Sache for providing this information. According to
Ivan, fire blight is currently a very "hot" issue in Switzerland. Only a
few species are listed because the original list of plant species included
those that are not monitored by ProMED-Mail. An international workshop on
fire blight is set for later this year (8-12 Oct 2001 -- 9th International
Workshop On Fire Blight, Napier, New Zealand. Contact: C.N. Hale,
